{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One learns how to avoid it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One becomes streetwise, if you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of the things was never volunteer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For instance, a day after our arrival, on the appel-- not the first day, the second day-- German officer comes along.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this-- the, the words are spoken by the blockalteste and the kapo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't bother to talk to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, all people under the age of 16, step out of the line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you're going to go on easier work in a jam factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not step out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many did-- not everybody who were under 16.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were never seen daylight again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the last-- last day of appell that they had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So obviously, one learned never to volunteer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never to stand on the front, not in the back, and not in the side-- always be in the middle somewhere.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is useful when you stand for hours on appell-- and I'm talking already of Buchenwald, later times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when it's very cold, if two people stand behind you, you don't get the freezing snow or the, or the wind on you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somebody else gets it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it is amazing how quickly a person can adopt to inhumane, unreasonable conditions and still say, fine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We will make it somehow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at this point, I think I must explain that the survival of anybody depended on their luck-- [YIDDISH SPEECH,] as they say in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a matter of luck at what age you were deported, at which camp you got to-- you know, many other things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was a certain amount of things which you could do yourself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first and the foremost condition was never to give up.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
